               <p>I am a <rs id="t17780603-52-viclabel253" type="occupation">baker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17780603-52-victim419 t17780603-52-viclabel253"></join>; I can only speak to the property.</p>
