                     <interp inst="t17780603-52-verdict255" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder1s"></interp>
               Guilty of stealing to the value of 10 d.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
